      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……私も入っていい？\n麻奈さんとのこと、芽衣ちゃんから聞いたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ can I come in‚ too?\nMei told me about what happened with Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……\n入って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura…\nCome on in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
