    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃんと{user}さんが\n麻奈さんの言葉を伝えてくれるよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei and {user} will\nrelay everything Mana is saying to you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "きっと麻奈さんも、琴乃ちゃんに話したいこと\n沢山あるんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure that Mana also has\nlots of things she wants to tell you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 55.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "…………そうなのかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really think so?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "…………私も、話したいと思う\nけど、話しちゃダメな気もする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I do want to talk to her.\nBut I get the feeling we shouldn’t talk.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 64.33333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.33333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 65.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "はっきりとは分からない。けど今お姉ちゃんと話したら\n今までの私じゃいられなくなる。そんな気がするの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know for sure‚ but if I talk to my sister‚\nI’m worried that I’ll stop being the person I’ve been. I just get that sense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shed-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "03-2d",
      "startTime": 76.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_01-2d.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 76.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "私がいると分かったら\nきっと張り詰めたものが切れてしまう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If she finds out that I’m still here‚\nI’m sure something will break inside of her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 83.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 83.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "私ね、お姉ちゃんがいなくなったからこそ\nここまでやってこれたと思っている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Listen‚ I think it’s because my sister left\nthat I was able to get this far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの想いを\n私が代わりに叶えるために……って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister’s wishes…\nI believed that I had to make them come true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "……うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 97
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、お姉ちゃんがそのことをどう思っているか\n聞いてしまったら……何かが終わってしまう気がする",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don’t know how my sister actually feels about that.\nAnd if I were to find out… I’m worried that something might end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "さくらが言うことは分かる\n私だって話したい。でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand what you’re saying‚ Sakura.\nI want to talk to her‚ too. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 110.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02/sud_vo_adv_main_01_17_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "…………本当に、それでいいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you really okay with leaving things this way?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "02-2d",
      "startTime": 114.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
